snippet.title: NEW Armajet Early Access Trailer - Worldwide reveal at GAMESCOM 2018 with RAZER!
snippet.description:
Check out the all-new ARMAJET Early Access trailer exclusively revealed worldwide at GAMESCOM 2018 with RAZER!

** The future of multiplayer takes flight with ARMAJET — sign up for Early Access on https://www.armajet.com and fly into the fray! **

*MORE INFORMATION*

• Armajet is now cross-platform, cross-play compatible! Play with your friends across all iOS, Android, and PC devices
• Play Armajet in 120+ FPS capable devices—exactly what you expect from high-octane jetpack deathmatch action
• All new Spectator Mode (V1) with more refined camera controls and force-follow functions

See you in the arena, commanders!

*STAY CONNECTED WITH ARMAJET*

⇢Like Armajet on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Armajet
⇢Follow Armajet on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Armajet
⇢Join the Armajet discussion on Discord: discord.gg/armajet
⇢Official SBM Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/armajet
⇢Official ARMAJET: https://www.armajet.com
⇢Official Super Bit Machine: https://www.superbitmachine.com
